                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Powell</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-07-03"><hi rend="italic">July 3,
                                1902</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Hay states that the U. S. S. <hi rend="italic">Marietta</hi> has
                            been ordered to Cape Haitian, touching at Port au Prince.)</p>
